Functional Requirements

Secure user registration and authentication.

Smart, AI-driven form field prediction.

Chat-based user interface for guidance.

Backend logic for processing and validation.

Administrative panel for monitoring queries.

Non-Functional Requirements

Fast and responsive interface across devices.

Secure configuration via .env file.

Quick setup with Docker and virtual environments.

Multilingual and accessibility-friendly support.

Technology Stack

Frontend: HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript

Backend: Python (Flask or FastAPI)

Database: JSON/CSV for MVP; extendable to SQL/NoSQL

AI/NLP: spaCy, NLTK, Transformers

Deployment: Docker, Virtualenv, Nginx

Target Users

General public seeking simplified access to civic services

Government bodies aiming to automate public engagement.